channel.title: Eohr - Cream [classic auxy future bass]
channel.description:
Hello Auxians!
I'm back again, for a while. I've been quite busy this year and not had as much inspiration/motivation to create, but I finally managed to finish some music I've been working on for way too long. This track is a collaboration with my good friend Jack, who sent me a few chord and drum loops. I worked on them and fleshed out a full song.
https://soundcloud.com/eohr/cream-with-jikkityjek
I hope you all enjoy it.
